  We would appreciate that the following two articles be
  referenced to describe the registration method in all publications
  of data analyzed using the MNI_AutoReg package:

      DL Collins, P Neelin, TM Peters and AC Evans,
      Automatic 3D Inter-Subject Registration of MR Volumetric 
      Data in Standardized Talairach Space,
      Journal of Computer Assisted Tomography, 18(2) p192-205, 1994

      DL Collins, CJ Holmes, TM Peters and AC Evans",
      Automatic 3D model-based neuro-anatomical segmentation
      Human Brain Mapping, 3(3) p 190-208, 1995
